For this year's Mother's Day celebration, pamper the most important woman in our lives with a sumptuous meal in the comfort of home!
•
@crystaljadesg has launched a special Parents' Day promotion from 1 May to 30 June 2020. Choose from a variety of set menus, available for both takeaway and delivery. Prices start from S$78 (2 pax) to S$498 (10 pax).
•
Pictured above is Crystal Jade La Mian Xiao Long Bao's Set Menu for 4 (S$168):
•
1. Steamed Siew Mai topped with Pearl Abalone 珍珠鲍鱼烧卖
2. Fried Rice with Prawn, Chicken & Ham 上海三鲜炒饭
3. Fish Paste Thick Soup with Coriander and Shredded Mushroom in Xihu Style 西湖鱼茸羮
4. Braised Chicken with Taro 鲜奶香芋焖鸡
5. Sautéed Prawn in Hot and Sour Sauce 京烧虾球
6. Poached White Cabbage in Superior Broth with Whole Garlic 高汤蒜子浸津白
•
Complimentary dessert: Black Sesame Glutinous Rice Dumpling in Ginger Soup 姜茶芝麻汤圆
•
FREE island-wide delivery with any order of Parents' Day set menu via @deliveroo_sg
•
Many thanks to @crystaljadesg and @sixthsensepr @hsianming for sending over this menu.
•
#SGunited #circuitbreakersg #stayhomesg #crystaljadesg #sgfood #sgfoodies #sgig #igsg #instasg #whati8today #singaporefood

@aromacookery Okay! I'll take a look. Thank you! Usually on Sundays, I will try to take a break and order in. Will definitely order from Crystal Jade one of these weeks. Also intend to order @nanhwachong1927 which is a family fav for pomfret hotpot. 😋
@purple__olive mmm pomfret hotpot! Sounds good, I wanna try that too! Thanks for the rec!
@aromacookery be sure to add in remarks to "add soup" and request for less bones for elderly and kids. They will really adhere to your request. 👍
